{"id":3544,"date":"2024-05-16T15:43:53","date_gmt":"2024-05-16T08:43:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/?p=3544"},"modified":"2024-05-16T15:49:04","modified_gmt":"2024-05-16T08:49:04","slug":"chua-hang-chau-doc-chon-tam-linh-noi-tieng-voi-doi-ran-than-khong-lo","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/chua-hang-chau-doc-chon-tam-linh-noi-tieng-voi-doi-ran-than-khong-lo\/","title":{"rendered":"Ch\u00f9a Hang Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c \u2013 Ch\u1ed1n t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i r\u1eafn th\u1ea7n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong><em>V\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t An Giang linh thi\u00eang n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i ch\u00f9a mang v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, g\u1eafn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n huy\u1ec1n b\u00ed, trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00f9a Hang Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ch\u00f9a Hang Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c \u2013 Ch\u1ed1n t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i r\u1eafn th\u1ea7n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ecda l\u1ea1c tr\u00ean s\u01b0\u1eddn n\u00fai Sam, thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, t\u1ec9nh An Giang, ch\u00f9a Ph\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110i\u1ec1n hay<strong>&nbsp;ch\u00f9a Hang<\/strong>&nbsp;Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t danh lam th\u1eafng c\u1ea3nh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf mi\u1ec1n T\u00e2y Nam B\u1ed9.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><strong>Ch\u00f9a Hang<\/strong><\/em>&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 1840 \u2013 1850 do b\u00e0 L\u00ea Th\u1ecb Th\u01a1 (c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 b\u00e0 Th\u1ee3), ph\u00e1p danh Di\u1ec7u Thi\u1ec7n s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp. V\u00ec c\u1ea3m m\u1ebfn \u00e2n \u0111\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Ni s\u01b0 Di\u1ec7u Thi\u1ec7n, \u00f4ng Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00f4ng hay t\u00ean th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Ng\u1ecdc Cang c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n quanh v\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 quy\u00ean g\u00f3p ti\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a, x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i ch\u00f9a v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1885. \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 1937, H\u00f2a th\u01b0\u1ee3ng Th\u00edch Hu\u1ec7 Thi\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh cho tr\u00f9ng tu, n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u00f9a l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay, ch\u00f9a \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tu b\u1ed5, s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn3.ivivu.com\/2022\/12\/chua-hang-an-giang2-ivivu.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn3.ivivu.com\/2022\/12\/chua-hang-an-giang2-ivivu.jpg\" alt=\"chua-hang-an-giang2-ivivu\" class=\"wp-image-390216\" title=\"\"><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p><em>Ch\u00f9a Hang<\/em>\u00a0g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi khung c\u1ea3nh m\u00e1t m\u1ebb, n\u1eb1m gi\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng gian trong l\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao b\u1ecdc b\u1edfi r\u1eebng c\u00e2y xanh th\u1eb3m. \u0110\u1ec3 tham quan v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ec5 Ph\u1eadt t\u1ea1i ch\u00f9a, du kh\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i \u0111i theo nh\u1eefng b\u1eadc thang x\u00e2y b\u1eb1ng kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1, d\u1ed1c kh\u00e1 cao, h\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 \u0111i. \u0110o\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111i m\u1ed9t h\u01a1i, r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ee9ng l\u1ea1i, h\u00edt th\u1edf kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong l\u00e0nh, ng\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00ecn c\u1ea3nh ch\u00f9a cao v\u1eddi v\u1ee3i hay ng\u1eafm c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1eb1ng r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn, bao la b\u00e1t ng\u00e1t gi\u00fap du kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 qu\u00ean \u0111i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi m\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-3.jpg\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"650\" height=\"488\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3545\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-3.jpg 650w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-3-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y du kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng h\u00e0ng m\u00e1i ng\u00f3i \u0111\u1ecf t\u01b0\u01a1i, b\u1eaft m\u1eaft h\u00e0i h\u00f2a c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0u g\u1ed7 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ch\u00f9a t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5m c\u00fang. Nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t ch\u1ea1m tr\u1ed5 tr\u00ean t\u1eebng g\u1ed1c c\u1ed9t trong ch\u00f9a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ec9 m\u1ec9 v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho ng\u00f4i ch\u00f9a.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3549\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-5-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p>Trong khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean ch\u00f9a c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec7n th\u1edd Ph\u1eadt Di L\u1eb7c, t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Quan Th\u1ebf \u00c2m B\u1ed3 T\u00e1t v\u00e0 b\u1ed1n v\u1ecb th\u1ea7n H\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p tr\u00f4ng xu\u1ed1ng ch\u00e2n n\u00fai. T\u1eeb s\u00e2n ch\u00f9a Ph\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110i\u1ec1n, du kh\u00e1ch b\u1ed1n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m m\u1eaft ra d\u00e3y n\u00fai cao \u1edf xa xa hay c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00e1t ng\u00e1t d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00e2n n\u00fai.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-4.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"668\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3546\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-4.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-4-600x401.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-390467\">C\u00e1c b\u1eadc thang d\u1eabn t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n n\u00fai l\u00ean ch\u00f9a Hang. \u1ea2nh: petrotimes.vn.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec7n, c\u00e1c ng\u00f3c ng\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a hang s\u00e2u, v\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf ch\u00f9a Hang c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1edd. Hai b\u00ean l\u1ed1i \u0111i c\u00f3 t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1eafn \u2013 linh v\u1eadt trong truy\u1ec1n thuy\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ch\u00f9a Hang Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c. Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang ho\u00e0ng trang nghi\u00eam v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee9c ho\u00e0nh phi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ed3i ch\u1ea1m kh\u1eafc tinh x\u1ea3o.<a href=\"https:\/\/cdn3.ivivu.com\/2022\/12\/chuahang4-ivivu.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chuahang4.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chuahang4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3547\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chuahang4.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chuahang4-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-390218\">Hai b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1eafn l\u1edbn Thanh X\u00e0 v\u00e0 B\u1ea1ch X\u00e0 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n thuy\u1ebft. \u1ea2nh: Vietnamoi.<a href=\"https:\/\/cdn3.ivivu.com\/2022\/12\/chua-Hang-ivivu-5.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn3.ivivu.com\/2022\/12\/chua-Hang-ivivu-6.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"650\" height=\"488\" src=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3548\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-2.jpg 650w, https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/05\/chua-Hang-2-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-390469\">Pho t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an tr\u00ed trong l\u00f2ng n\u00fai. \u1ea2nh: truyenhinhdulich.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong l\u00e0nh m\u00e1t m\u1ebb c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 y\u00ean b\u00ecnh, t\u00e2m t\u1ecbnh trong ch\u00ednh l\u00f2ng m\u00ecnh. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u b\u00ecnh an, may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 t\u00e0i l\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\">\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n tham kh\u1ea3o<\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Ivivu &#8211; C\u1ea9m nang du l\u1ecbch<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>V\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5t An Giang linh thi\u00eang n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i ch\u00f9a mang v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, g\u1eafn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n huy\u1ec1n b\u00ed, trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00f9a Hang Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c. Ch\u00f9a Hang Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c \u2013 Ch\u1ed1n t\u00e2m linh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i r\u1eafn th\u1ea7n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u1ecda l\u1ea1c tr\u00ean [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":3550,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[131,81],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3544"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3544"}],"version-history":[{"count":2